Package fillrbust

Class FillRBustGame

  • java.lang.Object
    • fillrbust.FillRBustGame
  • class FillRBustGame
extends java.lang.Object
    Play the game FillRBust.
    • maintains the state of the game: players, dice, card, game state,
    • enacts the rules
    • reports back to the GUI (which actually drives the game)

    • Nested Class Summary

      Nested Classes 
      Modifier and Type Class Description
      static class  FillRBustGame.STATES
      Game STATES determine the actions and options according to the rules of the game.
      Those actions and options are codified in the update method.
